            <title><![CDATA[香港近三分之一BNO签证申请者年龄在18岁以下]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>香港近三分之一BNO签证申请者是18岁以下人群。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>据《南华早报》星期三（11月9日）报道，在</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>14.2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>万</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>名</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>BNO签证申请者中，有3.86万人来自18岁以下人群，其中仅16%的申请在英国提交。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>另外，35岁至44岁</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>BNO签证申请者</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>有3.26万人，其中13%在英国提交申请。年龄在45岁至54岁之间的人士提交了2.78万份申请，其中14%在英国提交。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<section id="imu"><div id="dfp-ad-imu1">
        
</div>


</section>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>在申请</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>BNO</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>签证的人群中，25岁至54岁的香港人占55%，即7.81万人。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>移民顾问表示，数据证实了他们亲眼目睹的情况，即年龄在30至50岁之间的香港人计划移民，以便让他们的子女能在英国上学。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>英国内政部8月份公布的数据显示，自该计划推出以来，截至今年6月，共有133124名香港人获得了入籍许可。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<div id="innity-in-post"></div>
<div id="dfp-ad-midarticlespecial">
        
</div>



<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>香港大学社会工作及社会行政学系讲座叶兆辉</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>教授估计，自该计划开始以来，有5万个家庭计划或已经移居英国。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>他警告称，由于专业人士占很大一部分，无论是专业技术还是离开的人数，都不容易被取代。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>目前，只有1997年6月30日即香港回归前一天之前出生的人有资格独立申请</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>BNO</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>签证。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>据估计，在香港750万居民中，有540万人拥有资格申请</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>BNO</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>签证。成功的申请</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>BNO</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>签证的人士及其家属在英国生活、工作和学习长达五年之后可申请成为英国公民。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>英国计划于本月放宽</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>BNO</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>签证申请条件，允许在1997年7月1日或之后出生、父母至少一方具有</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>BNO</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>签证身份的香港人使用父母身份申请在英国定居。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
      


